 ou bien il butinera d’un sujet à l’autre, au gré de ses inclinations. Sa lecture l’étonnera parfois ; elle l’éclairera souvent. Les auteurs prennent ici soin de s’adresser à des non spécialistes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aMathematics. 7aMATHEMATICS / Probability & Statistics / General.2bisacsh1 aGodinot, Alain, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aPadieu, René, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aPont-Neuf, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020z978311075640140uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-2384-040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759823840423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759823840/original  a978-3-11-075640-1  EDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020c2016d2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK